{"id":953185108,"lang":"cpp","lang_name":"C++","time":"6 months, 3 weeks","timestamp":1684478953,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"3 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/953185108/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Integer to Roman","memory":"5.9 MB","code":"class Solution {\npublic:\n    string intToRoman(int num) {\n        string roman=\"\";\n        while(num>=1000){\n            num-=1000;\n            roman+=\"M\";\n        }\n        if(num>=900){\n            num-=900;\n            roman+=\"CM\";\n        }\n        if(num>=500){\n            num-=500;\n            roman+=\"D\";\n        }\n        if(num>=400){\n            num-=400;\n            roman+=\"CD\";\n        }\n        while(num>=100){\n            num-=100;\n            roman+=\"C\";\n        }\n        if(num>=90){\n            num-=90;\n            roman+=\"XC\";\n        }\n        if(num>=50){\n            num-=50;\n            roman+=\"L\";\n        }\n        if(num>=40){\n            num-=40;\n            roman+=\"XL\";\n        }\n        while(num>=10){\n            num-=10;\n            roman+=\"X\";\n        }\n        if(num>=9){\n            num-=9;\n            roman+=\"IX\";\n        }\n        if(num>=5){\n            num-=5;\n            roman+=\"V\";\n        }\n        if(num>=4){\n            num-=4;\n            roman+=\"IV\";\n        }\n        while(num>=1){\n            num--;\n            roman+=\"I\";\n        }\n        return(roman);\n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"integer-to-roman","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
